description: 1995 21' Procraft V200C Boat with Procraft Steel Trailer. Fishing/powerboat, was completely gone through in the last 2 years.  The Hull was checked and tested.  All new Marine grade Tan carpet installed front to back of boat 2 years ago. Bow seats are new/re-covered in tan matching vinyl and added padding to both.  Complete new set of gauges,  speedo, tach, fuel level, trim and volt meter.  Hummingbird depth gauge, digital.   Lowrance HDMI-4 fishfinder, depth finder is one year old. New Steering wheel and new Helm.  Both helm cables are newer and recently cleaned and lubed, front to back at motor.  New large Navy anchor and 100 foot line, comes out custom hole in front with chrome metal cover.   AM/FM/CD player added with waterproof cover, and two new marine speakers. All switches, Lights work.  Main power switch is brand new. Engine has had the lower end rebuilt 16 months ago, new seals, new water pump all set.  Engine was gone/checked through recently, and the engine originally had low hours to start with, clean and runs great.  New trim pump installed 6 months ago. Boat will run 50-55 MPH at full throttle.  Comes with front mounted trolling motor with foot control, and plugs into front electrical section.   This trolling motor is currently not attached to the boat, but can be put back on. Engine is a Mercury 2.5 liter (best of the V6) at 200 HP.  Runs on only Synthetic pro oil.  At time of refit, new chrome marine locks for the compartments were added and new tan straps for all lids.  Two live wells with drain and pump to fill both. New Bilge pump with automatic float.  Has new Black Bimini top added.  Comes with a 2 year old custom made full boat all weather cover and straps, plus engine cover as well.   Cover is showing its age.  Runs as good as new, slow speeds to full throttle.  Well taken care of. Trailer is also made by Procraft and was made for this boat.  It's steel, has some surface rust that was sealed 6 months ago and painted to help protect.  Good tires, carpet nice on rails and new wiring was done 2 years ago, but I have the odd bulb out once in awhile.  New front butterfly roller and new winch with strap added.  2 years ago, just about everything was replaced or rebuilt.  Was made for not only fishing but pleasure cruising.  Its been used only about 1-2  times in the past 6 months, it was a fresh water boat for most of its life, only the last year and a half did it see the ocean, maybe 10-12 times. Located in Palm Harbor near East Lake High School. Serious inquiries only please.
